            <ECUC-PARAM-CONF-CONTAINER-DEF UUID="be6052de-b673-41c8-a8b5-88246d31386a">
              <SHORT-NAME>EcucPostBuildVariants</SHORT-NAME>
              <DESC>
                <L-2 L="EN">Collection of toplevel PostBuildSelectable variants. The PredefinedVariants linked inside this container will determine how many PostBuildSelectableVariants exist. If this container exist the name pattern for initialization of BSW modules will be &lt;Mip&gt;_Config_&lt;PredefinedVariant.shortName&gt;. If this container does not exist the name pattern for initialization of BSW modlues will be &lt;Mip&gt;_Config.</L-2>
              </DESC>
